# Staff — Internal Endpoints
# UC-022: BFF resolves which tenant a Google account belongs to (staff login)
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up           (start PostgreSQL + Pub/Sub emulator)
#   2. pnpm --filter @beloauto/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @beloauto/backend run dev
#
# REST Client environment: select "local" in VS Code status bar

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}
@sub = google-sub-example-staff-123

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get staff info for a known active Google OAuth ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-oauth?googleOAuthId={{sub}}

###

### Get staff info for an inactive (deactivated) staff member
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-oauth?googleOAuthId=google-sub-deactivated-staff

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROR CASES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 400 — Missing googleOAuthId query parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-oauth

###

### 404 — Google account not registered as staff in any tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-oauth?googleOAuthId=unknown-sub-not-staff
